text: Sony Playstation 2 is allowed by the University firewall
FTP and SFTP servers are allowed by the University firewall
Guests' network is rate-limited to 5 Mb/s per user
PC-Telephone is allowed by the University firewall
Everquest is blocked by the University firewall

If a student is in obvious violations of copyright law by using a room's wired connection (ie ResNet) to distribute copyrighted materials, the room's connection will be disabled, and the issue could be sent to Housing Student Judicial Affairs
All network traffic passing in or out of Brown's network is monitored by intrusion detection system for signs of compromises
CIS restricts traffic that is known to cause damage to the network or hosts on it, such as NETBIOS
Battlenet is allowed by the University firewall
RHIT-OPEN will work in labs, classrooms and residence halls but does not allow the user to access the internal Rose-Hulman network
Elements of network security currently include the following four solutions: Network Border Infrastructure System, Intrusion Prevention System, Firewalls and Custom Unit Firewalls
Students 10 GB a day download quotas are on 10 AM to Midnight
